            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Strict Documentation Requirements</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Swiss banks require extensive documentation including residence permits, proof of address, employment contracts, and source of funds. Missing or incorrect documents cause delays or rejections.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
